## Limitations

This report is based on available data up to October 2023 and may not capture the most recent developments in the energy sector. Additionally, the complexity of global energy markets means that not all factors contributing to the energy shortage can be fully explored in this brief report. Further research and analysis are recommended for a more comprehensive understanding.